properties.description:
The name of the field In case of an action parameter dialog, this is the fieldname only <code><pre>
{
    property: <fieldname>
}
</pre></code> In case of a create dialog, the concatenation of the entity and fieldname has to be provided <code><pre>
{
    property: <entity>::<fieldname>
}
</pre></code>

